##Read the guidance

Read the guidance booklets on making a Lasting Power of Attorney and filling in the forms:

$D
[Download 'Guidance for making a health and welfare Lasting Power of Attorney' (PDF, 1.32MB)](http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/global/forms/opg/lpa-guidance-health-and-welfare.pdf "Guidance for making a health and welfare Lasting Power of Attorney (PDF 1.32MB)"){:rel="external"}

[Download 'Guidance for making a property and financial affairs Lasting Power of Attorney' (PDF, 1.35MB)](http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/global/forms/opg/lpa-guidance-property-affairs.pdf "Guidance for making a property and financial affairs Lasting Power of Attorney (PDF, 1.35MB)"){:rel="external"}
$D

##Download the forms you need 

###Health and welfare

To make a health and welfare Lasting Power of Attorney, fill in the following forms:

$D
[Download 'Health and welfare Lasting Power of Attorney form' (PDF, 570KB)](http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/global/forms/opg/lasting-power-of-attorney-health-and-welfare-the-instrument.pdf "Health and welfare Lasting Power of Attorney form (PDF, 570KB)"){:rel="external"}

[Download 'Continuation sheets for a health and welfare Lasting Power of Attorney' (PDF, 390KB)](http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/global/forms/opg/hw-continuation-sheet.pdf "Continuation sheets for a health and welfare Lasting Power of Attorney (PDF, 390KB)"){:rel="external"}
$D

###Property and financial affairs

To make a property and financial affairs Lasting Power of Attorney, fill in the following forms:

$D
[Download 'Property and financial affairs Lasting Power of Attorney form' (PDF, 650KB)](http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/global/forms/opg/lasting-power-of-attorney-property-and-financial-affairs-the-instrument.pdf "Property and financial affairs Lasting Power of Attorney form (PDF, 650KB)"){:rel="external"}

[Download 'Continuation sheets for a property and financial affairs Lasting Power of Attorney' (PDF, 380KB)](http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/global/forms/opg/pfa-continuation-sheets.pdf "Continuation sheets for a property and financial affairs Lasting Power of Attorney (PDF, 380KB)"){:rel="external"}
$D

##Download large print forms and guidance

You can also download large print versions of the guidance and forms:

$D
**Health and welfare**  
[Download 'Guidance for making a health and welfare Lasting Power of Attorney - large print version' (PDF, 3.89MB)](http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/global/forms/opg/health-welfare-guidance-large-print-1109.pdf "Guidance for making a health and welfare Lasting Power of Attorney - large print version (PDF, 3.89MB)"){:rel="external"}

[Download 'Health and welfare Lasting Power of Attorney form - large print version' (PDF, 590KB)](http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/global/forms/opg/lpa-hw-lrg-print-info-1009.pdf "Health and welfare Lasting Power of Attorney form - large print version (PDF, 590KB)"){:rel="external"}

[Download 'Continuation sheets for a health and welfare Lasting Power of Attorney - large print version' (PDF, 410KB)](http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/global/forms/opg/lpa-hw-continuation-sheets-lrg-print-1009.pdf "Continuation sheets for a health and welfare Lasting Power of Attorney - large print version (PDF, 410KB)"){:rel="external"}  
$D
  
$D
**Property and financial affairs**  
[Download 'Guidance for making a property and financial affairs Lasting Power of Attorney - large print version' (PDF, 3.98MB)](http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/global/forms/opg/property-financial-affairs-guidance-large-print-1009.pdf "Guidance for making a property and financial affairs Lasting Power of Attorney - large print version (PDF, 3.98MB)"){:rel="external"}

[Download 'Property and financial affairs Lasting Power of Attorney form - large print version' (PDF, 600KB)](http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/global/forms/opg/lpa-pfa-lrg-print-1009.pdf "Property and financial affairs Lasting Power of Attorney form - large print version (PDF, 600KB)"){:rel="external"}

[Download 'Continuation sheets for a property and financial affairs Lasting Power of Attorney - large print version (PDF, 400KB)](http://www.justice.gov.uk/downloads/global/forms/opg/lpa-pfa-continuation-sheets-lrg-print-1009.pdf "Continuation sheets for a property and financial affairs Lasting Power of Attorney - large print version (PDF, 400KB)"){:rel="external"}
$D

##Get the forms posted to you

If you don't have a printer, you can [ask for the forms to be posted to you.](https://forms.direct.gov.uk/forms/form/777/en/opg-lasting_power_of_attorney_lpa "ask for the forms to be posted to you"){:rel="external"}

You should get your forms within 14 days.
